public class StorageObjectsChunk
extends java.lang.Object

Stores a "chunk" of StorageObjects returned from a list command - this particular chunk may or may not include all the objects available in a bucket. This class contains an array of objects and a the last key name returned by a prior call to the method StorageService.listObjectsChunked(String, String, String, long, String).
